    {
      "id": "node-b0a80c8495",
      "title": "終端内容分類ポワン",
      "body": "根まで追跡されたX上の終端投稿を、保存可能な content_class と確認対象 component に分類し、必要な子ポワンへ渡す神経ポワン。返信連鎖、引用連鎖、投稿でどころ判定は親側で済んだものとして扱い、ここでは終端投稿の中身だけを見る。RAG、意味検索、矛盾判定、人格推定は行わない。\n\n分類入力は terminal_post_envelope として受け取る。必須項目は run_id / trace_id / terminal_post_id / terminal_post_url / author_idまたはscreen_name / text / created_at / fetch_status / parent_trace / discovery_path / urls / media_items / card / fetched_at。parent_trace には元投稿から終端投稿までの edge_type(quote, reply, repost, card, external) と step_index を順序付き配列で残す。\n\ncontent_class は次の優先で決める。\n- unavailable: 終端投稿が削除、非公開、凍結、認証不可、年齢・地域制限、rate limit、ネットワーク失敗、HTML/API解析不能などで本文や素材を確認できない。\n- mixed: image / video / youtube / news_or_article / external_link のうち2種類以上の確認対象を含む。\n- youtube: YouTube URL、youtu.be、youtube.com、YouTubeカード、埋め込みURLを含む。\n- news_or_article: ニュース・記事らしい外部URL、記事カード、媒体ドメイン、article抽出対象URLを含む。\n- image: X画像または画像添付のみを含む。\n- video: X動画、GIF動画、動画カードのみを含む。\n- external_link: YouTubeでも記事でもない外部URLを含む。現時点では専用子ポワンがないため、URL証拠と未処理理由を保存して後続拡張口として残す。\n- text_only: URLやメディアを持たず、本文だけ確認できる。\n\nDBには classification_result として run_id, trace_id, terminal_post_id, terminal_post_url, author, text_hash, text_excerpt, content_class, component_flags, media_items_json, urls_json, routing_targets_json, evidence_json, discovery_path_json, fetch_status, terminal_reason, retryable, classified_at を残す。mixed の時は component_results を子ポワン単位で追記できる形にする。\n\nJSONLには terminal_content_classified / route_requested / route_skipped / child_result_recorded / terminal_unavailable を1イベント1行で残す。各行には event_ts, run_id, trace_id, terminal_post_id, content_class, components, child_title, status, error_type, retryable, artifact_paths, evidence_urls を含める。\n\nrunsログには人が追える短い要約を残す。終端投稿URL、分類、発見経路、起動した子ポワン、スキップ理由、取得不能理由、保存先パス、失敗フェーズを記録する。本文全文や大きいメディア本体はログへ直書きせず、DBキー、JSONLキー、ファイルパス、sha256で参照する。\n\n証拠保存ルールとして、X投稿IDとcanonical URLを最優先キーにし、短縮前raw_urlと展開後expanded_urlを両方保存する。メディアはoriginal_url, media_key, mime, size, sha256, local_path, source_entity_indexを残す。発見経路は上書きせず、親から受け取った parent_trace に分類時の発見根拠を append する。取得不能でも、到達しようとしたURL、HTTP status、API error、発生フェーズ、retryable を保存する。\n\n振り分けは、text_only と unavailable は自分の分類結果だけ保存して子へ渡さない。image は画像内容確認ポワン、video は動画内容確認ポワン、youtube はYouTube内容確認ポワン、news_or_article はニュース本文確認ポワンへ渡す。mixed は含まれるcomponentごとに該当する子をすべて起動し、子ごとの成功・失敗を独立して保存する。external_link は現時点では route_skipped として external_link_unhandled を保存し、将来の外部リンク確認ポワン追加に備える。",
      "powanKind": "nerve",
      "code": "from __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport hashlib\nimport json\nimport sys\nfrom collections.abc import Mapping, Sequence\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\nfrom urllib.parse import urlparse\n\nCHILD_IMAGE = {\"childId\": \"node-5cd6c85247\", \"title\": \"画像内容確認ポワン\", \"component_type\": \"image\"}\nCHILD_VIDEO = {\"childId\": \"node-9575d22dbe\", \"title\": \"動画内容確認ポワン\", \"component_type\": \"video\"}\nCHILD_YOUTUBE = {\"childId\": \"node-de37593461\", \"title\": \"YouTube内容確認ポワン\", \"component_type\": \"youtube\"}\nCHILD_NEWS = {\"childId\": \"node-50607708e4\", \"title\": \"ニュース本文確認ポワン\", \"component_type\": \"news_or_article\"}\n\nDEFAULT_JSONL_PATH = \"data/runs/terminal_content_events.jsonl\"\nDEFAULT_RUNS_LOG_PATH = \"data/runs/terminal_content_runs.log\"\n\nURL_KEYS = (\n    \"url\",\n    \"raw_url\",\n    \"rawUrl\",\n    \"expanded_url\",\n    \"expandedUrl\",\n    \"final_url\",\n    \"finalUrl\",\n    \"display_url\",\n    \"displayUrl\",\n    \"card_url\",\n    \"cardUrl\",\n)\nPOST_ID_KEYS = (\"terminal_post_id\", \"post_id\", \"postId\", \"tweet_id\", \"tweetId\", \"status_id\", \"statusId\")\nPOST_URL_KEYS = (\"terminal_post_url\", \"post_url\", \"postUrl\", \"tweet_url\", \"tweetUrl\", \"status_url\", \"statusUrl\")\nAUTHOR_KEYS = (\"author\", \"author_id\", \"authorId\", \"screen_name\", \"screenName\", \"username\", \"user\")\nTEXT_KEYS = (\"text\", \"full_text\", \"fullText\", \"body\", \"content\", \"tweet_text\", \"tweetText\")\nMEDIA_URL_KEYS = (\n    \"original_url\",\n    \"originalUrl\",\n    \"media_url\",\n    \"mediaUrl\",\n    \"media_url_https\",\n    \"mediaUrlHttps\",\n    \"image_url\",\n    \"imageUrl\",\n    \"playback_url\",\n    \"playbackUrl\",\n    \"video_url\",\n    \"videoUrl\",\n    \"url\",\n)\nMEDIA_TYPE_KEYS = (\"type\", \"media_type\", \"mediaType\", \"kind\")\nMEDIA_KEY_KEYS = (\"media_key\", \"mediaKey\", \"x_media_key\", \"xMediaKey\", \"id\")\n\nUNAVAILABLE_STATUSES = {\n    \"deleted\",\n    \"not_found\",\n    \"unavailable\",\n    \"private\",\n    \"protected\",\n    \"suspended\",\n    \"auth_required\",\n    \"login_required\",\n    \"forbidden\",\n    \"rate_limited\",\n    \"timeout\",\n    \"network_error\",\n    \"parse_error\",\n    \"html_parse_error\",\n    \"api_error\",\n}\nRETRYABLE_REASONS = {\"rate_limited\", \"timeout\", \"network_error\", \"api_error\", \"http_500\", \"http_502\", \"http_503\", \"http_504\"}\nYOUTUBE_DOMAINS = {\"youtube.com\", \"www.youtube.com\", \"m.youtube.com\", \"music.youtube.com\", \"youtu.be\", \"www.youtu.be\"}\nX_DOMAINS = {\"x.com\", \"www.x.com\", \"twitter.com\", \"www.twitter.com\", \"mobile.twitter.com\"}\nIMAGE_EXTENSIONS = {\".jpg\", \".jpeg\", \".png\", \".webp\", \".gif\", \".bmp\", \".avif\"}\nVIDEO_EXTENSIONS = {\".mp4\", \".mov\", \".m4v\", \".webm\", \".m3u8\", \".ts\"}\nARTICLE_DOMAIN_HINTS = {\n    \"nhk.or.jp\",\n    \"news.yahoo.co.jp\",\n    \"yahoo.co.jp\",\n    \"asahi.com\",\n    \"mainichi.jp\",\n    \"yomiuri.co.jp\",\n    \"nikkei.com\",\n    \"sankei.com\",\n    \"tokyo-np.co.jp\",\n    \"bbc.com\",\n    \"cnn.com\",\n    \"reuters.com\",\n    \"apnews.com\",\n    \"bloomberg.com\",\n    \"theguardian.com\",\n    \"nytimes.com\",\n    \"washingtonpost.com\",\n}\n\n\ndef classify_terminal_content(input_json: Any | None = None, *, options: Mapping[str, Any] | None = None) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Classify a traced terminal X post and build child route payloads.\"\"\"\n    payload = normalize_json_value(input_json)\n    if not isinstance(payload, Mapping):\n        payload = {\"terminal_post_envelope\": payload}\n    opts = build_options(payload, options)\n    envelope = terminal_envelope(payload)\n    now = now_iso()\n\n    text = first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), TEXT_KEYS)\n    urls = normalize_urls(payload, envelope)\n    media_items = normalize_media_items(payload, envelope)\n    fetch_status, terminal_reason, retryable = terminal_availability(payload, envelope)\n    flags = build_component_flags(urls, media_items, envelope)\n    content_class = choose_content_class(flags, text, fetch_status, terminal_reason)\n\n    if content_class == \"unavailable\" and not terminal_reason:\n        terminal_reason = \"no_content_found\" if not text and not urls and not media_items else \"terminal_unavailable\"\n    if terminal_reason and not retryable:\n        retryable = terminal_reason in RETRYABLE_REASONS\n\n    trace_id = trace_value(payload, envelope, \"trace_id\") or stable_hash([terminal_post_url(payload, envelope), now])\n    run_id = trace_value(payload, envelope, \"run_id\") or trace_id\n    terminal_post_id = first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), POST_ID_KEYS) or post_id_from_url(terminal_post_url(payload, envelope))\n    terminal_url = terminal_post_url(payload, envelope)\n    author = first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), AUTHOR_KEYS)\n\n    route_requests, route_skips = build_route_decisions(\n        content_class=content_class,\n        payload=payload,\n        envelope=envelope,\n        flags=flags,\n        urls=urls,\n        media_items=media_items,\n        run_id=run_id,\n        trace_id=trace_id,\n        terminal_post_id=terminal_post_id,\n        terminal_post_url=terminal_url,\n    )\n    evidence = build_evidence_json(payload, envelope, urls, media_items, route_requests, route_skips)\n\n    classification_result = {\n        \"run_id\": run_id,\n        \"trace_id\": trace_id,\n        \"terminal_post_id\": terminal_post_id,\n        \"terminal_post_url\": terminal_url,\n        \"author\": author,\n        \"text_hash\": sha256_text(text) if text else \"\",\n        \"text_excerpt\": compact(text, int(opts[\"textExcerptLimit\"])),\n        \"content_class\": content_class,\n        \"component_flags\": flags,\n        \"media_items_json\": media_items,\n        \"urls_json\": urls,\n        \"routing_targets_json\": route_requests,\n        \"route_skips_json\": route_skips,\n        \"evidence_json\": evidence,\n        \"discovery_path_json\": discovery_path(envelope),\n        \"parent_trace_json\": parent_trace(envelope),\n        \"fetch_status\": fetch_status,\n        \"terminal_reason\": terminal_reason,\n        \"retryable\": retryable,\n        \"classified_at\": now,\n    }\n\n    events = build_events(classification_result, route_requests, route_skips, now)\n    artifact_paths = persist_logs(events, classification_result, opts, route_requests, route_skips)\n    return {\n        \"ok\": content_class != \"unavailable\" or bool(terminal_reason),\n        \"status\": \"skipped\" if content_class in {\"text_only\", \"external_link\", \"unavailable\"} else \"routed\",\n        \"content_class\": content_class,\n        \"classification_result\": classification_result,\n        \"route_requests\": route_requests,\n        \"route_skips\": route_skips,\n        \"events\": events,\n        \"artifact_paths\": artifact_paths,\n        \"runs_log_summary\": runs_summary(classification_result, route_requests, route_skips),\n    }\n\n\ndef build_component_flags(urls: list[dict[str, Any]], media_items: list[dict[str, Any]], envelope: Mapping[str, Any]) -> dict[str, bool]:\n    image_items = image_candidates(urls, media_items)\n    video_items = video_candidates(urls, media_items)\n    youtube_items = [item for item in urls if is_youtube_url(best_url(item))]\n    article_items = [item for item in urls if is_article_url(item)]\n    external_items = [item for item in urls if is_external_url(best_url(item)) and not is_youtube_url(best_url(item)) and not is_article_url(item)]\n    flags = {\n        \"has_text\": bool(first_text(envelope, TEXT_KEYS)),\n        \"image\": bool(image_items),\n        \"video\": bool(video_items),\n        \"youtube\": bool(youtube_items),\n        \"news_or_article\": bool(article_items),\n        \"external_link\": bool(external_items),\n    }\n    flags[\"mixed\"] = sum(1 for key in (\"image\", \"video\", \"youtube\", \"news_or_article\", \"external_link\") if flags[key]) > 1\n    return flags\n\n\ndef choose_content_class(flags: Mapping[str, bool], text: str, fetch_status: str, terminal_reason: str) -> str:\n    if fetch_status in UNAVAILABLE_STATUSES or terminal_reason:\n        return \"unavailable\"\n    components = [key for key in (\"image\", \"video\", \"youtube\", \"news_or_article\", \"external_link\") if flags.get(key)]\n    if len(components) > 1:\n        return \"mixed\"\n    if components:\n        return components[0]\n    if text.strip():\n        return \"text_only\"\n    return \"unavailable\"\n\n\ndef build_route_decisions(\n    *,\n    content_class: str,\n    payload: Mapping[str, Any],\n    envelope: Mapping[str, Any],\n    flags: Mapping[str, bool],\n    urls: list[dict[str, Any]],\n    media_items: list[dict[str, Any]],\n    run_id: str,\n    trace_id: str,\n    terminal_post_id: str,\n    terminal_post_url: str,\n) -> tuple[list[dict[str, Any]], list[dict[str, Any]]]:\n    route_requests: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    route_skips: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    base = {\n        \"run_id\": run_id,\n        \"trace_id\": trace_id,\n        \"terminal_post_id\": terminal_post_id,\n        \"terminal_post_url\": terminal_post_url,\n        \"terminal_post_envelope\": dict(envelope),\n        \"content_class\": content_class,\n        \"component_flags\": dict(flags),\n        \"evidence_urls\": evidence_urls_from_sources(payload, envelope, urls),\n    }\n\n    if content_class == \"unavailable\":\n        route_skips.append(skip_record(\"unavailable\", \"terminal_unavailable\", base))\n        return route_requests, route_skips\n    if content_class == \"text_only\":\n        route_skips.append(skip_record(\"text_only\", \"no_child_needed\", base))\n        return route_requests, route_skips\n\n    if flags.get(\"image\"):\n        items = image_candidates(urls, media_items)\n        route_requests.append(route_record(CHILD_IMAGE, base, {\"image_items\": items}))\n    if flags.get(\"video\"):\n        items = video_candidates(urls, media_items)\n        route_requests.append(route_record(CHILD_VIDEO, base, {\"video_items\": items}))\n    if flags.get(\"youtube\"):\n        items = [item for item in urls if is_youtube_url(best_url(item))]\n        route_requests.append(route_record(CHILD_YOUTUBE, base, {\"youtube_urls\": items}))\n    if flags.get(\"news_or_article\"):\n        items = [item for item in urls if is_article_url(item)]\n        route_requests.append(route_record(CHILD_NEWS, base, {\"article_urls\": items}))\n    if flags.get(\"external_link\"):\n        external_items = [item for item in urls if is_external_url(best_url(item)) and not is_youtube_url(best_url(item)) and not is_article_url(item)]\n        route_skips.append(skip_record(\"external_link\", \"external_link_unhandled\", base, {\"external_urls\": external_items}))\n    return route_requests, route_skips\n\n\ndef route_record(child: Mapping[str, str], base: Mapping[str, Any], extra: Mapping[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    payload = {**base, **extra}\n    return {\n        \"childId\": child[\"childId\"],\n        \"child_title\": child[\"title\"],\n        \"component_type\": child[\"component_type\"],\n        \"status\": \"route_requested\",\n        \"payload\": payload,\n    }\n\n\ndef skip_record(component_type: str, reason: str, base: Mapping[str, Any], extra: Mapping[str, Any] | None = None) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return {\n        \"component_type\": component_type,\n        \"status\": \"route_skipped\",\n        \"skip_reason\": reason,\n        \"payload\": {**base, **(extra or {})},\n    }\n\n\ndef build_events(classification: Mapping[str, Any], routes: list[dict[str, Any]], skips: list[dict[str, Any]], event_ts: str) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    base = {\n        \"event_ts\": event_ts,\n        \"run_id\": classification.get(\"run_id\"),\n        \"trace_id\": classification.get(\"trace_id\"),\n        \"terminal_post_id\": classification.get(\"terminal_post_id\"),\n        \"terminal_post_url\": classification.get(\"terminal_post_url\"),\n        \"content_class\": classification.get(\"content_class\"),\n        \"components\": active_components(classification.get(\"component_flags\") or {}),\n        \"evidence_urls\": evidence_url_list(classification.get(\"evidence_json\") or {}),\n    }\n    events = [{**base, \"event\": \"terminal_content_classified\", \"status\": \"classified\"}]\n    for route in routes:\n        events.append({**base, \"event\": \"route_requested\", \"child_title\": route.get(\"child_title\"), \"component_type\": route.get(\"component_type\"), \"status\": \"requested\"})\n    for skip in skips:\n        events.append({**base, \"event\": \"route_skipped\", \"component_type\": skip.get(\"component_type\"), \"status\": \"skipped\", \"skip_reason\": skip.get(\"skip_reason\")})\n    if classification.get(\"content_class\") == \"unavailable\":\n        events.append({**base, \"event\": \"terminal_unavailable\", \"status\": \"unavailable\", \"terminal_reason\": classification.get(\"terminal_reason\"), \"retryable\": classification.get(\"retryable\")})\n    return events\n\n\ndef persist_logs(\n    events: list[dict[str, Any]],\n    classification: Mapping[str, Any],\n    opts: Mapping[str, Any],\n    routes: Sequence[Mapping[str, Any]],\n    skips: Sequence[Mapping[str, Any]],\n) -> list[str]:\n    if not opts.get(\"writeLogs\", True):\n        return []\n    paths: list[str] = []\n    jsonl_path = str(opts.get(\"jsonlPath\") or \"\").strip()\n    runs_path = str(opts.get(\"runsLogPath\") or \"\").strip()\n    if jsonl_path:\n        for event in events:\n            append_jsonl(jsonl_path, event)\n        paths.append(jsonl_path)\n    if runs_path:\n        append_line(runs_path, runs_summary(classification, routes, skips))\n        paths.append(runs_path)\n    return paths\n\n\ndef runs_summary(classification: Mapping[str, Any], routes: Sequence[Mapping[str, Any]], skips: Sequence[Mapping[str, Any]]) -> str:\n    route_names = \",\".join(str(route.get(\"child_title\") or route.get(\"component_type\")) for route in routes) or \"-\"\n    skip_reasons = \",\".join(str(skip.get(\"skip_reason\")) for skip in skips) or \"-\"\n    return (\n        f\"{classification.get('classified_at')} run={classification.get('run_id')} trace={classification.get('trace_id')} \"\n        f\"post={classification.get('terminal_post_id')} url={classification.get('terminal_post_url')} \"\n        f\"class={classification.get('content_class')} routes={route_names} skips={skip_reasons} \"\n        f\"reason={classification.get('terminal_reason') or '-'} retryable={classification.get('retryable')}\"\n    )\n\n\ndef terminal_availability(payload: Mapping[str, Any], envelope: Mapping[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str, bool]:\n    status = first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), (\"fetch_status\", \"fetchStatus\", \"status\", \"availability\"))\n    status = normalize_reason(status)\n    reason = first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), (\"terminal_reason\", \"terminalReason\", \"unavailable_reason\", \"unavailableReason\", \"error_type\", \"errorType\"))\n    reason = normalize_reason(reason)\n    if not reason and status in UNAVAILABLE_STATUSES:\n        reason = status\n    retryable = bool_value(first_value_from_sources((envelope, payload), (\"retryable\", \"can_retry\", \"canRetry\")))\n    if not retryable and reason in RETRYABLE_REASONS:\n        retryable = True\n    return status, reason, retryable\n\n\ndef terminal_envelope(payload: Mapping[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    value = payload.get(\"terminal_post_envelope\") or payload.get(\"terminalPostEnvelope\") or payload.get(\"terminal\") or payload\n    return dict(value) if isinstance(value, Mapping) else {}\n\n\ndef normalize_urls(payload: Mapping[str, Any], envelope: Mapping[str, Any]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    raw_items: list[Any] = []\n    for source in (envelope, payload):\n        for key in (\"urls\", \"expanded_urls\", \"expandedUrls\", \"external_urls\", \"externalUrls\"):\n            value = source.get(key) if isinstance(source, Mapping) else None\n            if isinstance(value, list):\n                raw_items.extend(value)\n        entities = source.get(\"entities\") if isinstance(source, Mapping) else None\n        if isinstance(entities, Mapping):\n            value = entities.get(\"urls\")\n            if isinstance(value, list):\n                raw_items.extend(value)\n        card = source.get(\"card\") if isinstance(source, Mapping) else None\n        if isinstance(card, Mapping):\n            raw_items.append(card)\n    out: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    seen: set[str] = set()\n    terminal_url = terminal_post_url(payload, envelope)\n    for index, item in enumerate(raw_items):\n        record = normalize_url_item(item, index=index, terminal_url=terminal_url)\n        url = best_url(record)\n        if not url or same_url(url, terminal_url):\n            continue\n        key = canonical_url_key(url)\n        if key in seen:\n            continue\n        seen.add(key)\n        out.append(record)\n    return out\n\n\ndef normalize_url_item(item: Any, *, index: int, terminal_url: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    if isinstance(item, Mapping):\n        record = dict(item)\n    else:\n        record = {\"raw_url\": str(item)}\n    raw_url = first_text(record, URL_KEYS)\n    expanded_url = first_text(record, (\"expanded_url\", \"expandedUrl\", \"final_url\", \"finalUrl\", \"url\", \"raw_url\", \"rawUrl\"))\n    record.setdefault(\"raw_url\", raw_url or expanded_url)\n    record.setdefault(\"expanded_url\", expanded_url or raw_url)\n    record.setdefault(\"source_entity_index\", index)\n    record.setdefault(\"evidence_url\", terminal_url or raw_url or expanded_url)\n    record.setdefault(\"url_domain\", domain_of(best_url(record)))\n    record.setdefault(\"url_kind\", infer_url_kind(record))\n    return json_safe(record)\n\n\ndef normalize_media_items(payload: Mapping[str, Any], envelope: Mapping[str, Any]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    raw_items: list[Any] = []\n    for source in (envelope, payload):\n        for key in (\"media_items\", \"mediaItems\", \"media\", \"photos\", \"videos\"):\n            value = source.get(key) if isinstance(source, Mapping) else None\n            if isinstance(value, list):\n                raw_items.extend(value)\n        attachments = source.get(\"attachments\") if isinstance(source, Mapping) else None\n        if isinstance(attachments, Mapping):\n            value = attachments.get(\"media\") or attachments.get(\"media_items\")\n            if isinstance(value, list):\n                raw_items.extend(value)\n        entities = source.get(\"extended_entities\") or source.get(\"extendedEntities\") if isinstance(source, Mapping) else None\n        if isinstance(entities, Mapping) and isinstance(entities.get(\"media\"), list):\n            raw_items.extend(entities[\"media\"])\n    out: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    terminal_url = terminal_post_url(payload, envelope)\n    for index, item in enumerate(raw_items):\n        if not isinstance(item, Mapping):\n            continue\n        record = dict(item)\n        media_type = normalize_reason(first_text(record, MEDIA_TYPE_KEYS))\n        media_url = first_text(record, MEDIA_URL_KEYS)\n        record.setdefault(\"media_type\", media_type)\n        record.setdefault(\"original_url\", media_url)\n        record.setdefault(\"x_media_key\", first_text(record, MEDIA_KEY_KEYS))\n        record.setdefault(\"source_entity_index\", index)\n        record.setdefault(\"evidence_url\", terminal_url or media_url)\n        out.append(json_safe(record))\n    return out\n\n\ndef image_candidates(urls: list[dict[str, Any]], media_items: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    items: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    for item in media_items:\n        media_type = normalize_reason(first_text(item, MEDIA_TYPE_KEYS))\n        media_url = first_text(item, MEDIA_URL_KEYS)\n        if media_type in {\"photo\", \"image\", \"animated_gif_image\"} or has_extension(media_url, IMAGE_EXTENSIONS):\n            items.append(item)\n    for url in urls:\n        if has_extension(best_url(url), IMAGE_EXTENSIONS) and not any(best_url(url) == first_text(item, MEDIA_URL_KEYS) for item in items):\n            items.append({\"original_url\": best_url(url), \"source_entity_index\": url.get(\"source_entity_index\"), \"evidence_url\": url.get(\"evidence_url\"), \"source_url_record\": url})\n    return items\n\n\ndef video_candidates(urls: list[dict[str, Any]], media_items: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    items: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    for item in media_items:\n        media_type = normalize_reason(first_text(item, MEDIA_TYPE_KEYS))\n        media_url = first_text(item, MEDIA_URL_KEYS)\n        if media_type in {\"video\", \"animated_gif\", \"gif\"} or has_extension(media_url, VIDEO_EXTENSIONS):\n            items.append(item)\n    for url in urls:\n        if has_extension(best_url(url), VIDEO_EXTENSIONS) and not any(best_url(url) == first_text(item, MEDIA_URL_KEYS) for item in items):\n            items.append({\"playback_url\": best_url(url), \"source_entity_index\": url.get(\"source_entity_index\"), \"evidence_url\": url.get(\"evidence_url\"), \"source_url_record\": url})\n    return items\n\n\ndef is_youtube_url(url: str) -> bool:\n    domain = domain_of(url)\n    return domain in YOUTUBE_DOMAINS or domain.endswith(\".youtube.com\")\n\n\ndef is_article_url(item: Mapping[str, Any]) -> bool:\n    url = best_url(item)\n    domain = domain_of(url)\n    text = \" \".join(str(item.get(key) or \"\") for key in (\"type\", \"kind\", \"url_kind\", \"card_type\", \"cardType\", \"title\", \"description\"))\n    lower = text.lower()\n    if any(word in lower for word in (\"article\", \"news\", \"headline\", \"press\")):\n        return True\n    return any(domain == hint or domain.endswith(\".\" + hint) for hint in ARTICLE_DOMAIN_HINTS)\n\n\ndef is_external_url(url: str) -> bool:\n    domain = domain_of(url)\n    return bool(domain) and domain not in X_DOMAINS and not domain.endswith(\".twitter.com\") and not domain.endswith(\".x.com\")\n\n\ndef infer_url_kind(record: Mapping[str, Any]) -> str:\n    url = best_url(record)\n    if is_youtube_url(url):\n        return \"youtube\"\n    if has_extension(url, IMAGE_EXTENSIONS):\n        return \"image\"\n    if has_extension(url, VIDEO_EXTENSIONS):\n        return \"video\"\n    return \"external_link\" if is_external_url(url) else \"internal\"\n\n\ndef build_evidence_json(payload: Mapping[str, Any], envelope: Mapping[str, Any], urls: list[dict[str, Any]], media_items: list[dict[str, Any]], routes: list[dict[str, Any]], skips: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return {\n        \"terminal_post_url\": terminal_post_url(payload, envelope),\n        \"terminal_post_id\": first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), POST_ID_KEYS),\n        \"parent_trace\": parent_trace(envelope),\n        \"discovery_path\": discovery_path(envelope),\n        \"raw_urls\": [item.get(\"raw_url\") for item in urls if item.get(\"raw_url\")],\n        \"expanded_urls\": [item.get(\"expanded_url\") for item in urls if item.get(\"expanded_url\")],\n        \"media\": media_items,\n        \"route_components\": [route.get(\"component_type\") for route in routes],\n        \"route_skips\": skips,\n    }\n\n\ndef build_options(payload: Mapping[str, Any], options: Mapping[str, Any] | None) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    raw = merge_dicts(payload.get(\"options\") if isinstance(payload.get(\"options\"), Mapping) else {}, options or {})\n    return {\n        \"writeLogs\": raw.get(\"writeLogs\", raw.get(\"write_logs\", True)) is not False,\n        \"jsonlPath\": raw.get(\"jsonlPath\") or raw.get(\"jsonl_path\") or DEFAULT_JSONL_PATH,\n        \"runsLogPath\": raw.get(\"runsLogPath\") or raw.get(\"runs_log_path\") or DEFAULT_RUNS_LOG_PATH,\n        \"textExcerptLimit\": raw.get(\"textExcerptLimit\") or raw.get(\"text_excerpt_limit\") or 240,\n    }\n\n\ndef append_jsonl(path_value: str, event: Mapping[str, Any]) -> None:\n    path = Path(path_value)\n    path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with path.open(\"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\", newline=\"\\n\") as fh:\n        fh.write(json.dumps(json_safe(event), ensure_ascii=False, sort_keys=True) + \"\\n\")\n\n\ndef append_line(path_value: str, text: str) -> None:\n    path = Path(path_value)\n    path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with path.open(\"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\", newline=\"\\n\") as fh:\n        fh.write(text.rstrip() + \"\\n\")\n\n\ndef terminal_post_url(payload: Mapping[str, Any], envelope: Mapping[str, Any]) -> str:\n    return first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), POST_URL_KEYS)\n\n\ndef parent_trace(envelope: Mapping[str, Any]) -> list[Any]:\n    value = envelope.get(\"parent_trace\") or envelope.get(\"parentTrace\") or []\n    return value if isinstance(value, list) else []\n\n\ndef discovery_path(envelope: Mapping[str, Any]) -> list[Any]:\n    value = envelope.get(\"discovery_path\") or envelope.get(\"discoveryPath\") or []\n    return value if isinstance(value, list) else []\n\n\ndef evidence_urls_from_sources(payload: Mapping[str, Any], envelope: Mapping[str, Any], urls: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> list[str]:\n    return unique_strings([terminal_post_url(payload, envelope), *[str(item.get(\"evidence_url\") or \"\") for item in urls], *[best_url(item) for item in urls]])\n\n\ndef evidence_url_list(evidence: Mapping[str, Any]) -> list[str]:\n    return unique_strings([evidence.get(\"terminal_post_url\"), *listify(evidence.get(\"raw_urls\")), *listify(evidence.get(\"expanded_urls\"))])\n\n\ndef active_components(flags: Mapping[str, Any]) -> list[str]:\n    return [key for key in (\"image\", \"video\", \"youtube\", \"news_or_article\", \"external_link\") if bool(flags.get(key))]\n\n\ndef trace_value(payload: Mapping[str, Any], envelope: Mapping[str, Any], key: str) -> str:\n    return first_text_from_sources((envelope, payload), (key, camel_case(key)))\n\n\ndef first_text_from_sources(sources: Sequence[Mapping[str, Any]], keys: Sequence[str]) -> str:\n    for source in sources:\n        value = first_text(source, keys)\n        if value:\n            return value\n    return \"\"\n\n\ndef first_value_from_sources(sources: Sequence[Mapping[str, Any]], keys: Sequence[str]) -> Any:\n    for source in sources:\n        if not isinstance(source, Mapping):\n            continue\n        for key in keys:\n            if key in source and source[key] not in (None, \"\"):\n                return source[key]\n    return None\n\n\ndef first_text(record: Any, keys: Sequence[str]) -> str:\n    if not isinstance(record, Mapping):\n        return \"\"\n    for key in keys:\n        value = record.get(key)\n        if value not in (None, \"\") and not isinstance(value, (dict, list, tuple)):\n            text = str(value).strip()\n            if text:\n                return text\n    return \"\"\n\n\ndef best_url(record: Mapping[str, Any]) -> str:\n    return first_text(record, (\"expanded_url\", \"expandedUrl\", \"final_url\", \"finalUrl\", \"raw_url\", \"rawUrl\", \"url\", \"card_url\", \"cardUrl\"))\n\n\ndef domain_of(url: str) -> str:\n    try:\n        return urlparse(url).netloc.lower().split(\"@\").pop().split(\":\")[0]\n    except Exception:\n        return \"\"\n\n\ndef path_of(url: str) -> str:\n    try:\n        return urlparse(url).path.lower()\n    except Exception:\n        return \"\"\n\n\ndef has_extension(url: str, extensions: set[str]) -> bool:\n    path = path_of(url)\n    return any(path.endswith(ext) for ext in extensions)\n\n\ndef post_id_from_url(url: str) -> str:\n    parts = [part for part in path_of(url).split(\"/\") if part]\n    for index, part in enumerate(parts):\n        if part in {\"status\", \"statuses\"} and index + 1 < len(parts):\n            return parts[index + 1]\n    return \"\"\n\n\ndef canonical_url_key(url: str) -> str:\n    parsed = urlparse(url)\n    return f\"{parsed.scheme.lower()}://{parsed.netloc.lower()}{parsed.path}\".rstrip(\"/\")\n\n\ndef same_url(left: str, right: str) -> bool:\n    return bool(left and right and canonical_url_key(left) == canonical_url_key(right))\n\n\ndef normalize_reason(value: str) -> str:\n    return str(value or \"\").strip().lower().replace(\"-\", \"_\").replace(\" \", \"_\")\n\n\ndef bool_value(value: Any) -> bool:\n    if isinstance(value, bool):\n        return value\n    if isinstance(value, (int, float)):\n        return bool(value)\n    return str(value or \"\").strip().lower() in {\"1\", \"true\", \"yes\", \"y\", \"retryable\"}\n\n\ndef sha256_text(text: str) -> str:\n    return hashlib.sha256(text.encode(\"utf-8\")).hexdigest()\n\n\ndef stable_hash(values: Sequence[Any]) -> str:\n    return hashlib.sha256(json.dumps(list(values), ensure_ascii=False, sort_keys=True).encode(\"utf-8\")).hexdigest()[:16]\n\n\ndef compact(value: Any, limit: int = 240) -> str:\n    text = \" \".join(str(value or \"\").split())\n    return text if len(text) <= limit else text[: max(0, limit - 1)] + \"...\"\n\n\ndef camel_case(value: str) -> str:\n    parts = value.split(\"_\")\n    return parts[0] + \"\".join(part[:1].upper() + part[1:] for part in parts[1:])\n\n\ndef merge_dicts(*items: Any) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    out: dict[str, Any] = {}\n    for item in items:\n        if isinstance(item, Mapping):\n            out.update(dict(item))\n    return out\n\n\ndef listify(value: Any) -> list[Any]:\n    return value if isinstance(value, list) else []\n\n\ndef unique_strings(values: Sequence[Any]) -> list[str]:\n    out: list[str] = []\n    for value in values:\n        text = str(value or \"\").strip()\n        if text and text not in out:\n            out.append(text)\n    return out\n\n\ndef json_safe(value: Any) -> Any:\n    if isinstance(value, Mapping):\n        return {str(key): json_safe(item) for key, item in value.items()}\n    if isinstance(value, list):\n        return [json_safe(item) for item in value]\n    if isinstance(value, tuple):\n        return [json_safe(item) for item in value]\n    if isinstance(value, Path):\n        return str(value)\n    return value\n\n\ndef normalize_json_value(value: Any) -> Any:\n    if value is None:\n        return {}\n    if isinstance(value, (Mapping, list)):\n        return value\n    if isinstance(value, str):\n        text = value.strip()\n        if not text:\n            return {}\n        path = Path(text)\n        if path.exists():\n            return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n        return json.loads(text)\n    return value\n\n\ndef load_json_arg(value: str) -> Any:\n    if not value or value == \"-\":\n        text = sys.stdin.read().strip()\n        return json.loads(text) if text else {}\n    return normalize_json_value(value)\n\n\ndef now_iso() -> str:\n    return datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat()\n\n\ndef run(input_json: Any = None, **kwargs: Any) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return classify_terminal_content(input_json, **kwargs)\n\n\ndef orchestrate(input_json: Any = None, **kwargs: Any) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return classify_terminal_content(input_json, **kwargs)\n\n\ndef main(argv: list[str] | None = None) -> int:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Classify terminal X post content and prepare child routes.\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--input-json\", default=\"-\", help=\"JSON string, JSON file path, or '-' for stdin.\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--no-logs\", action=\"store_true\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--jsonl-path\", default=DEFAULT_JSONL_PATH)\n    parser.add_argument(\"--runs-log-path\", default=DEFAULT_RUNS_LOG_PATH)\n    args = parser.parse_args(argv)\n    result = classify_terminal_content(\n        load_json_arg(args.input_json),\n        options={\n            \"writeLogs\": not args.no_logs,\n            \"jsonlPath\": args.jsonl_path,\n            \"runsLogPath\": args.runs_log_path,\n        },\n    )\n    print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n    return 0 if result.get(\"ok\") else 1\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    raise SystemExit(main())",
